    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You honestly won't believe how beautiful this ride is until you see it in person. I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like driving it off the lot for the first time! It runs like a total dream and has been pampered in the garage since day one. If you're looking for a car that's been truly loved and cared for, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
