    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a benchmark example of high-revving atmospheric induction. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering an 8,400 RPM redline and surgical throttle response. The chassis retains its original kinematic integrity, with the factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock providing precise torque vectoring. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission offers lightning-fast gear synchronization, while the carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof remains flawless. This specimen is mechanically impeccable, having undergone preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service to ensure peak operational longevity. Every seal, bushing, and fluid line is in showroom condition, presenting a rare opportunity for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. Zero accidents. Clean title. Full service history. Garage kept.",
      "price": 46500.0,
