    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in spectacular shape! Not a single scratch or ding to be found\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept and babied since day one. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
