    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the 996.2 evolution. Powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus valve timing, this naturally aspirated powerhouse delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The wide-body C4S architecture houses a sophisticated AWD system and the uprated braking system from the contemporary Turbo, including four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors. This specimen is in museum-grade condition, with a flawless underbody, pristine bore scores, and a factory-tight suspension. A rare find for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection and uncompromising performance.",
